  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p192682/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i1.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201110/usual31775.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>1、这山望着那山高 The grass is always greener on the other hill.</strong><br />\n\t人都是这山望着那山高，对自己的状况没有满意的时候。<br />\n\tAlmost all people see that the grass is greener on the other hill. They never feel satisfied with what they&rsquo;ve already got.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>2、上瘾get into one&rsquo;s blood</strong><br />\n\t说来也怪，很多不好的事往往会使人上瘾。<br />\n\tIt&rsquo;s astoundingly funny that many harmful things usually get into our blood.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>3、发牢骚 beef</strong><br />\n\t他坐在那里什么事也不干，总是发牢骚，真烦死人。<br />\n\tI&rsquo;m really bored stiff with his sitting there doing nothing but beefing.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>4、等不及了 champ at the bit</strong><br />\n\t咱们快点吧，孩子们都等不及了。<br />\n\tLet&rsquo;s shake the leg. The kids are champing at the bit.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>5、点头哈腰bow and scrape</strong><br />\n\t从她在老板前点头哈腰地那个模样，你就知道她是个什么人了。<br />\n\tFrom the way she&rsquo;s bowing and scraping in front of the boss, you&rsquo;ll know what sort of person she is.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>6、疯疯癫癫go gaga</strong><br />\n\t对他的话不要太在意了，他总是疯疯癫癫的。<br />\n\tDon&rsquo;t take what he says so seriously. He&rsquo;s always going gaga.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>7、说话不算数go back on one&rsquo;s words</strong><br />\n\t他那个人说话从不算数,我们可不能依靠他。<br />\n\tWe cannot account on him. He always goes back on his words.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>8、废话连篇beat one&rsquo;s gums</strong><br />\n\t谁喜欢坐在那里听你的废话连篇？<br />\n\tWho would enjoy sitting there listening to your beating your gums?</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>9、恩将仇报 bite the hand that feeds one</strong><br />\n\t你难道不知道她是个恩将仇报的人？<br />\n\tDon&rsquo;t you know she&rsquo;s the one that would bite the hand that feeds her?</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>10、不忍心not have the heart to do</strong><br />\n\t如果我是你，我可不忍心把孩子们就在家里没人照看<br />\n\tIf I were you, I wouldn&rsquo;t have the heart to leave the kids at home uncared for.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>11、勤快an eager beaver</strong><br />\n\t他特别勤快，从来没有闲着的时候。<br />\n\tHe&rsquo;s an eager beaver, never staying idle.</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p192682/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p192682\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p732147/\">本拉登也是学霸！《纽约时报》曝光拉登书单</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p738015/\">提高学习效率？澳洲学霸的4条铁律</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p737233/\">双语有声：你终将找到自己的节奏</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p738019/\">吃货必备：12个与食物有关的地道俚语</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p725717/\">敏感的“薪资”问题 英语可以这么答</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p738248/\">英国奇女子：一觉醒来英音变中国口音</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p737922/\">恋爱教学：调情的5个万能英文句型</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p738156/\">说多了都是泪：家长整教师的雷人语录</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p161331/\">新概念英语第一册Lesson 1  Excuse me</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736793/\">英国公司招人出奇招：来面试就给1000镑</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href